OL,4,CShrewsbury 24: Ricky Tomlinson would
OL,5,Cface jail again 'in a heartbeat'
OL,6, Actor Ricky Tomlinson has said he would
OL,7, face prison again "in a heartbeat" to
OL,8, stand up for workers' rights.
OL,10,FThe Liverpool star was one of the trade
OL,11,Funionists known as the Shrewsbury 24
OL,12,Fwho had their 1970s convictions for
OL,13,Fconspiracy overturned on Tuesday.
OL,15,FThe 81-year-old said he endured months
OL,16,Fof solitary confinement during his
OL,17,Ftwo-year sentence because he acted as a
OL,18,Fpolitical prisoner, but had no regrets.
OL,20,FHe said he did what he had to, adding:
OL,21,F"You've got to fight, haven't you?"
